description:
Umeya Tsubasa is a http://anidb.net/t1004 [judo] club member who moved to the soccer club after he fell in love with the club`s manager http://anidb.net/ch89596 [Moka]. After learning that Moka`s in love with http://anidb.net/ch89594 [Aoyama], he decided to support her love instead, stating that not every couple will ended up to marriage, and he only need to wait until that time.
